author: gordonsmith
msg: Falcon: Added <uptodate> logic for messages_en.properties and the various JAR files.
The 'main' target no longer does a clean because eventually it will be totally incremental and do nothing if nothing needs to be done.
The 'main' target now builds the sdk and the Javadoc (and, at the top-level, runs the tests).

msg: Now we are using JUnit4, can use expected=throwable.class for simple failure checks
